n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh_Hant_hk/News/TheSun/0501-00176-037b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh_Hant_hk%2FNews%2FTheSun%2F0501-00176-037b1.jpg&h=5cb3de5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9633ab1087b8612133485e5aa41ac017945ca427","tid":225280,"uid":13132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:25:07.000Z","msg":"大中華左膠中大都唔去，支那會執柒左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0128ab5fbc3f55c6eefebb7562d24bca7b4e3ef2","tid":225280,"uid":50719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:25:52.000Z","msg":"冷漠，徹底的無視，就是對六四集會最好的攻擊。下年最好提都唔好提。"},{"pid":"e4560a968d7d0b5501df85f6dd20207982ce5544","tid":225280,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:32:22.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f084211810435ffe708817fc362e83835f84f113","tid":225280,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冷漠，徹底的無視，就是對六四集會最好的攻擊。下年最好提都唔好提。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfed03c145fe2334f02ada16293ca5531210b2c8","tid":225280,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T18:02:23.000Z","msg":"64其實關香港咩事？<br />\n入侵國歷史又唔是香港歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又唔見成日口口聲聲返&ldquo;大陸&ldquo;（支那）班香港人走去羅湖深圳紀念下鳩叫下。"},{"pid":"7a7ee55f0432c6f7e293d5c0ff19e3f147e646b3","tid":225280,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T18:20:04.000Z","msg":"其實64算唔算青少年反共既第一關"},{"pid":"f304e79d4ee4f2b374a9b2f34a9d288a8ab382d0","tid":225280,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:46:42.000Z","msg":"香港年輕人厭中 你仲叫佢地幫中國人爭民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1c0b8240d